        <code>chmod 444 config.system.php</code>" from within the html/var directory.</p>
        <p>If you are feeling even more security conscious you could remove read access from those
        who don't need it: (substitute "apache" for the group your webserver runs as, probably one
        of apache, web, www or www-data) 
            <br />
            <code>chgrp apache config.system.php</code>
            <br />
        <code>chmod 440 config.system.php</code></p>
